    <p>{`I woke up the others. Laura, Kaitlin, and I began to hike up the wall in the morning twilight to where we had seen the sun set the previous night. None of us got much, if any sleep, and you could tell as we all looked and acted rather sleep deprived. But once up to our summit, we were all awestruck again as we watched the sun rise. It was absolutely beautiful!`}</p>
